Create resource bundle

create your resource bundle folder. Right click on your project select new>folder>expand you project name from the list>exapand src>choose main> give folder name resources
 so the path is /src/main/resources
 
 create one more folde inside resources name it as locale
 
 create your resource properties files in the locale folder. Default locale in this example is en
 
This proerty file is empty text file. Name the file as 
messages_en.properties
label.title=Login Page
label.firstName=First Name
label.lastName=Last Name
label.submit=Login


Create one more property file for fr locale
messages_fr.properties

label.title=Connectez-vous page
label.firstName=Pr\u00E9nom
label.lastName=Nom
label.submit=Connexion
